# What is Mocking?

Mocking means creating fake objects for testing.

Real Dependency:

```text
Service
   ↓
Database
```

Database not available?

Use Mock Object.

```text
Service
   ↓
Mock Database
```

---

# What is Moq?

Moq is a mocking framework for .NET.

Official Site:
[Moq GitHub Repository](https://github.com/devlooped/moq?utm_source=chatgpt.com)

Used to:

* Mock Interfaces
* Mock Services
* Mock Repositories
* Avoid Real Database Calls

