# NUnit vs Moq

| NUnit             | Moq                      |
| ----------------- | ------------------------ |
| Testing Framework | Mocking Framework        |
| Executes Tests    | Creates Fake Objects     |
| Uses Assertions   | Uses Setup & Verify      |
| Similar to JUnit  | Similar to Mockito(Java) |

